high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn left in front of the counter
Pick up the potato on the counter
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the fridge
Put the potato in the fridge, wait, pick up the potato from the fridge
Turn right, go forward, turn left at the counter
Put the potato on the counter
anns.task_desc: Cool a potato in the fridge and put it on the counter

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the stove on the left.
Pick up the potato from the back side of the counter.
Carry the potato a few steps to the left, to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the potato inside. Shut the door, then open it and take out the potato. Shut the door.
Carry the potato a few steps to the right, to the counter.
Place the potato on the front side of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Chill a potato and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the small counter space between the refrigerator and the stove, on your right.
Pick up the potato between the stove and the bowl, on the back of the counter.
Go to the refrigerator, directly to your left.
Place the potato in the refrigerator, on the, on the second shelf, to the left of the tomato, wait a moment for the potato to chill, then remove the potato from the refrigerator.
Turn to your right and go back tot he small counter space, between the refrigerator and the stove, on your left.
Place the potato in front of the knife, on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato on the kitchen counter.
